data.description: Looking for peace and quiet with not a neighbor in sight? You've found the right place. This 68.5 acres is covered in trees. No need to drive out of town to go hunting.. you can hunt of your front porch where deer will walk right up to the feeder giving you a perfect shot. This outstanding property has two living quarters on the property. One of them including a cozy living room with a tall unique fireplace, a kitchen, bathroom, laundry room, loft up stairs, with the backside of the house full of windows over looking your underground pool and hot tub. Walk across to the second living quarters where you will walk past your outdoor fireplace/patio area that is perfect for making homemade pizzas and relaxing with a fire burning listening to the peace and quiet. Once you walk into the second living quarters you will have beautiful glass doors that lead you into the garage that can easily fit two vehicles. This space doesn't have to be used as just a garage, but would also be great for an at home office, at home gym, another living area, and more (it has central heat&air). Off of this area is another bedroom. Walk on out of the glass doors up the stairs to a peaceful master bedroom area. The windows/views from this upstairs room are something you see off of movies. Right of of the stair case is a patio door where you can enjoy your coffee from up high and see the views of this beautiful place/outdoor pool. The views from the master bathroom are something you will have to see with your own eyes. Pictures don't do it justice. Stepping out of the shower to a large glass window with the outdoor views is a dream. That "natural lighting" everyone wants, is just what this bathroom has, but even better, it comes with a view! Navarro Mills Lake is just one mile from the property. You can get to Waco in just 40 minutes or less, and Dallas Forth Worth in under an hour and a half!
